@startuml
title Amonora v2 Bot - главное меню и верхний уровень навигации
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "Пользователь" as user
rectangle "bot/router.py\n_main_menu_keyboard()\n_main_menu_text()\n_send_main_menu()" as main_menu

rectangle "\"Моя подписка\"\nV2_MY_SUBSCRIPTION_CALLBACK\nv2_my_subscription_callback()\nrouter.py + _load_test_user_summary()\nbot/db.py + bot/public_subscription.py" as my_subscription

rectangle "\"Ключ\"\nV2_KEY_MENU_CALLBACK\nv2_key_menu_callback()\nrouter.py + _subscription_key_menu_keyboard()\nbot/public_subscription.py + bot/db.py" as key_menu

rectangle "\"Продлить\"\nV2_RENEW_CALLBACK\nv2_renew_callback()\nrouter.py + _renew_keyboard()\nbot/db.py + bot/utils/texts.py" as renew

rectangle "\"Информация\"\nV2_INFO_CALLBACK\nv2_info_callback()\nrouter.py + _info_keyboard()\nbot/utils/texts.py" as info

rectangle "\"Поддержка\"\nV2_SUPPORT_CALLBACK\nv2_support_callback()\nrouter.py + _support_keyboard()\nbot/utils/texts.py" as support

rectangle "\"Бонусная система\"\nV2_BONUS_CALLBACK\nv2_bonus_callback()\nrouter.py + _load_bonus_summary()\nbot/db.py + bot/keyboards/referrals.py" as bonus

rectangle "bot/db.py\nget_user_by_telegram_id()\nget_user_balance_summary()\nget_user_vpn_clients()\nget_user_referral_stats()" as bot_db
rectangle "bot/public_subscription.py\nget_or_create_public_subscription_page_url_for_user()\nbuild_public_subscription_happ_wrapper_url()\nget_public_subscription_bound_devices_for_user()" as public_subscription
rectangle "bot/utils/texts.py\nINFO_SCREEN_TEXT\nSUPPORT_SCREEN_TEXT\npayment text helpers" as texts
rectangle "bot/keyboards/referrals.py\nreferral_share_url()" as referrals_keyboard

user --> main_menu

main_menu --> my_subscription
main_menu --> key_menu
main_menu --> renew
main_menu --> info
main_menu --> support
main_menu --> bonus

my_subscription --> bot_db
my_subscription --> public_subscription

key_menu --> bot_db
key_menu --> public_subscription

renew --> bot_db
renew --> texts

info --> texts
support --> texts

bonus --> bot_db
bonus --> referrals_keyboard

note bottom of main_menu
Кнопки главного меню в router.py:
1. Моя подписка / Ключ
2. Продлить / Информация
3. Поддержка / Бонусная система
end note
@enduml
